trans-unit.source: Defines constants that represent areas of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeViewHitTestLocations> enumeration is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TreeViewHitTestInfo> class.
A position above the client portion of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> control.
A position below the client portion of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> control.
A position within the bounds of an image contained on a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A position in the indentation area for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A position on the text portion of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A position to the left of the client area of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> control.
A position in the client area of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> control, but not on a node or a portion of a node.
A position on the plus/minus area of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A position to the right of the client area of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeView"></xref> control.
A position to the right of the text area of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
A position within the bounds of a state image for a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TreeNode"></xref>.
